pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-kDTinF dTimTh pf-155_"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-156_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-157_"><p class="sc-ehCJOs iphVAH pf-158_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">No, we don't recommend using an electric blanket because over time it can have an adverse effect on the materials used inside the topper.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-crHmcD jDvJAM pf-160_"><button type="button" class="sc-jrQzAO eqVTRu pf-161_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="d7e1a243-c66a-4e18-be41-368ce9c233c9" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I use the topper on an adjustable bed?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d7e1a243-c66a-4e18-be41-368ce9c233c9" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-kDTinF dTimTh pf-163_"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-164_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-165_"><p class="sc-ehCJOs iphVAH pf-166_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Yes, all our toppers are suitable for adjustable beds. Please remember to check when selecting our toppers, the dimensions are compatible to that of your existing adjustable bed.<br></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-crHmcD jDvJAM pf-168_"><button type="button" class="sc-jrQzAO eqVTRu pf-169_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="d3f52a76-b241-40ab-b0c8-d206aa19f00d" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Why is keeping cool so important for getting a good night's sleep?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d